  <brief_title>Thromboembolic Complications Related to Asparaginase in Children With Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia (ALL) Treated According to NOPHO ALL 2008</brief_title>
  <official_title>Thromboembolic Complications Related to Asparaginase in Children With ALL Treated According to NOPHO ALL 2008</official_title>
